snippet.title: [Download] Star Revenge 8 Scepter of Hope - Release Trailer (v1.4)
snippet.description:
Yay, the "last" Star Revenge is done, also in an 1.4 version with some small improvements -no, that does not mean I stop with sm64, it's just the last SR game timeline based-
Download v1.4: https://drive.google.com/file/d/0Bzs1FL5re-t2SHJ3Mi1xcjZHMkU/view

Just saying, this hack is best played in sessions. The hack can get frustrating over time.

The hack has 121 stars, the usuall difficulty and the levels are mostly Touhou based. Credits are on the first sign ingame. You are also able to use the SR6.9 password in this hack, if you didn't got it play SR6.9 or beat the final boss of SR8 and you get it aswell!
The hack also comes with a map since this is an open world hack, so you can find quicker ways to get to the levels you want to.
Oh yeah, you could call this hack also Super Touhou 64 :P

Music in the video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7AB2Uhz4e8Q
